title: Bulletin de la Délégation pour l'Union Européenne
additional-notes: This is a French publication. Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US.

This appears to be the bulletin for a delegation of France's Assemblée Nationale.  Some library catalogs confuse the ISSN for this serial with the ISSN for the Assemblée Nationale's Bulletin des Commissions.
